Package: sendspin-service
Version: 0.1.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: any
Maintainer: Dutch Drone Squad <info@dutchdronesquad.nl>
Depends: systemd
Description: Sendspin playback service
 Standalone Sendspin playback service with a local HTTP ingest API.
 The service owns the Sendspin player endpoint and can be used by
 local voice plugins or other producers that submit WAV playback jobs.
